usage: build_humanize_voice_profile.py [-h] --sample-spec SAMPLE_SPEC
                                       --allowed-root ALLOWED_ROOT
                                       --profile-id PROFILE_ID
                                       [--scene {AUTO,COURSE,MODELING,RESEARCH,GENERAL}]
                                       --manifest-out MANIFEST_OUT
                                       --output OUTPUT [--format {json,text}]
                                       [--revision REVISION]
                                       [--source-date-epoch SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH]
                                       [--max-file-bytes MAX_FILE_BYTES]
                                       [--max-total-bytes MAX_TOTAL_BYTES]
                                       [--max-units MAX_UNITS]

Build a deterministic, evidence-bound Chinese Voice Profile. The builder
deliberately publishes only a small registry of mechanically rebuildable
features. It never embeds source prose in the profile. Samples that cannot be
decoded safely are audited and skipped instead of guessed.

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --sample-spec SAMPLE_SPEC
  --allowed-root ALLOWED_ROOT
  --profile-id PROFILE_ID
  --scene {AUTO,COURSE,MODELING,RESEARCH,GENERAL}
  --manifest-out MANIFEST_OUT
  --output OUTPUT
  --format {json,text}
  --revision REVISION
  --source-date-epoch SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH
  --max-file-bytes MAX_FILE_BYTES
  --max-total-bytes MAX_TOTAL_BYTES
  --max-units MAX_UNITS
